HAPPY_NEW_YEAR_2008 for CSS 
by S.T.A.L.K.E.R.(BY)

MAP INFORMATION:

Map Name: HAPPY_NEW_YEAR_2008
Map Type: DE (Bomb/Defuse) 
Release date: January 5th, 2008
Available Weapons: Standard 
Map Theme: New Year
Map's Time of Day: Night 
Maximum Players: 32
Custom Textures Used: yes
.NAV File Included (for bots and locations): yes

Details:
This is my remake of the Halo 2 map Turf. I decided to set it up as a de map since its so perfectly designed for that gametype. It has some lighting problems still, but i decided to just release it since im not getting anywhere trying to fix them hahaha. Specs:
34 spawns, 2 bomb zones, free-swinging doors (shoot them or run into them to push them open), ramps that drop into position when you touch them, 3D skybox, and obsessively detail, full buyzones, custom textures, and a few easter eggs.
Please visit Clan 5k3's studio for more Halo css maps and materials.

Map: de_gridlock
Author: Fubliz (Fred D.)
Web Site: http://TheeUnforgiveN.com

Info:

Gridlock is a Gears of War remake for CS:S, I felt that it would be fun to create the maps from GoW into CS:S to give those maps new aspects of game play. A lot of testing and game play mechanics went into creating Gridlock to fit the game style of Counter-strike verse Gears of Wars game style. I hope everyone enjoys it, there are new area's and different advantage points vs the Gears of War version. 

I give a lot of thanks to my alpha/beta testing team for giving me a lot on thoughts about the game play and design structure. They put a lot of hours into testing the map and giving constructive feed back.
